	<div class="innerpage_sections" id="childcare">
	<div class="top_title"><h2>ChildCare</h2></div>

	<div class="top_info">
	<p>There is a lot of vulnerable children in Tanzania whose future lives are evidently a game of chance. Uncertainity and lack of hope are still the major characteristics of a Tanzanian child, hence these children find themselfs in jeopardy most of the time. Historical backgrounds of the country and adherence of unnecessary traditional practices by some community members, are one of the significant causes of the set back of children's progress in Tanzania. Poverty and lack of education of most caretakers are one of the main reasons of children's rights' deprivation. According to a recent Unicef journal....? <a href="https://www.unicef.org/tanzania/media/2761/file/Journey%20of%20a%20Child%20in%20Tanzania.pdf" target="blank">Unicef on Children in Tanzania</a>. Recent studies show that there is still a big gap between poor and well-off families. Unfortunately, the poor families make the bigest part of the country's population. Children in poor families are deprived of their basic human rights. Right to education, right to food, shelter and clothing are just examples of what they lack. <a href="http://wbgfiles.worldbank.org/documents/hdn/ed/saber/supporting_doc/CountryReports/ECD/SABER_ECD_Tanzania_CR_Final_2012.pdf" target="blank">A pdf by WB</a> However, the existence of community based organizations like <a href="">Twiga Vision Tanzania</a> has become a relief for most families as they are now able to reach out for help in regard to the needs of their children and of the community as a whole. As a Twiga Vision Tanzania's Volunteer, through our Eager Volunteers' program, you have a lot to contribute in providing solutions for challenges facing children and women in Tanzania. We will place you at one of the following, depending on your choice; a Daycare School, a Primary School, an Orphanage centre and/or a health centre. All those are points you can meet the needs of children.<a href="contacts.php"> Book a volunteer placement with us today.</a> We will provide you with step by step guide on how to make your dream a reality.<a href="contacts.php"> Contact us to learn more </a>  Or <a href="index.php?#programs" class="program_back_link">Go back to previous section</a> </p>
	
	</div>

