	<div class="top_info">
	<p>Working with this program gives you an opportunity to directly or indirectly impact the health of women and children as our main targets. You can do this in many ways and scales. For example you can provide basic health education to groups of women and children or you can take a more serious role of working in a health centre and healping people directly. Moreover, by providing food and/or medical support to families in need, you will have directly impacted those individuals on their health issue as well.
